```c++
You can add your code example here
```

== Remarks ==
This function is used internally, and should not be used unless you have a specific need to ^designate^ ,,specify,, the audio driver you want to use.  You should normally use [[SDL_Init]]() or [[SDL_InitSubSystem]]().

